&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welsh Student Nurses must apply via the Student Streamlining Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for suitably qualified registered nurses to join the respiratory team on ward 11, YGC. This advert is for permanent positions, full or part time to suit. Ward 11 is an acute 24 bed respiratory ward where an acute non invasive ventilation service is also provided in up to 4 level 2 beds, this is predominantly nurse led, and extremely well supported by the Consultants. Degree level Non Invasive Ventilation training is offered to all our trained staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 10/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
